sentences: Anna David (born 2 December 1984) is a Danish R&B and soul singer.
Her debut album, simply titled Anna David, was released in Denmark in September 2005 and was certified Gold.
The lead single, Fuck Dig, held the #1 position on Danish single chart for twelve weeks and received the 'Payload Prize 2005' for being the most downloaded song of the year in Denmark.
